Desiree Gould https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Desiree_Gould 0 Desiree Joan Gould (born March 27, 1945) is an American theater, film and television actress, singer and dancer. She is known for her role in the 1983 slasher horror classic Sleepaway Camp. Desiree_Joan_Gould ( born March_27_,_1945 ) is an_American_theater_,_film_and_television_actress , singer_and_dancer .
